    "excerpt": "<p>Oh. I think you are referring the nameplate example. The \u201c// preview[\u2026]\u201d is actually not used by the program.<br>\n\u201cmainly\u201d means we also tried to be compatible with Thingiverse Customizer. You can refer it in <a href=\"https://customizer.makerbot.com/docs\" class=\"inline-onebox\">MakerBot Customizer</a>.<br>\nWe will provide a wiki for this later.</p>",
