        "cooked": "<p><a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/dantup\">@DanTup</a> Currently, the model displayed on the web is in STL, so we cannot bring colors with it (unless we use non-stand STL).<br>\nSupporting multi-color is already in our road map and it will be supported later.</p>",
